Tanzanite One Says 12,100-Carat Stone Discovered at Simanjiro in Tanzania

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-02-28T07:30:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/tanzanite-one-says-12-100-carat-stone-discovered-at-simanjiro-in-tanzania.html
  Tanzanite One Ltd . said it
discovered a 12,100-carat rough tanzanite stone at its project
in the Simanjiro district of Tanzania. It’s the third-largest
high-quality gemstone mined in the project’s 10-year operating
history, Tanzanite One said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Amanda Jordan in London at 
